'''三及第汤'''是[[客家菜|客家菜]]的一种，相传起源于[[清朝|清朝]]。
== 作法 ==
将[[猪|猪]]肉、猪肝、猪粉肠配上[[枸杞|枸杞]]叶或[[咸菜|咸菜]]等辅料熬制而成，猪肉、猪肝、猪粉肠象征着[[状元|状元]]、[[榜眼|榜眼]]、[[探花|探花]]，合称三及第，客家人喜欢将三及第汤与油腻的[[腌面|腌面]]搭配成为早餐。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://news.gmw.cn/newspaper/2013-06/14/content_1569517.htm|title = 客家美食三及第汤|accessdate = |author = |date = 2013-06-14|publisher = 光明网|archive-date = 2016-11-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161129224219/http://news.gmw.cn/newspaper/2013-06/14/content_1569517.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.mzta.gov.cn/info/shi/kjmc/2011/1114/2255.html|title = 三及第汤|accessdate = |author = |date = 2011-11-14|publisher = 梅州市旅游局|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161129231111/http://www.mzta.gov.cn/info/shi/kjmc/2011/1114/2255.html|archive-date = 2016-11-29|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

